  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.242545658601277         -6.6000          -152.20          -636.80
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.066157470982034          1.8002            41.51           173.70
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.037129008757578         -1.0103           -23.30           -97.48
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.166071251761637          4.5190           104.21           436.02
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

